/* Add this CSS to styles.css */
#nav-bar {
    background-color: #333;
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000; /* To ensure it appears above other elements */
}

.nav-link {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: inline-block;
}

.nav-link:hover {
    background-color: #ddd;
    color: black;
}

.nav-list {
    list-style-type: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center; /* Align items horizontally at the center */
}

.nav-list li {
    margin: 0 10px; /* Add space between each list item */
}

/* Media query */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .nav-link {
        padding: 10px;
    }
}
